<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<div type="elementDocumentation" xml:id="elem-seriesstmt" xmlns:ead="http://ead3.archivists.org/schema/" xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">
               <head>
                  <gi>seriesstmt</gi>
               </head>
               <div type="fullName">
                  <p xml:lang="eng">Series Statement</p>
               </div>
               <div type="summary">
                  <p>A child element of <gi>filedesc</gi> that groups information about the published monographic series to which an EAD instance belongs.</p>
               </div>
               <div type="mayContain">
                  <p>num, p, titleproper</p>
               </div>
               <div type="mayOccurWithin">
                  <p>filedesc</p>
               </div>
               <div type="attributes">
                  <p>
                     <list type="gloss">
                        <label>altrender</label>
                        <item>Optional</item>
                        <label>audience</label>
                        <item>Optional (values limited to: external, internal)</item>
                        <label>encodinganalog</label>
                        <item>Optional</item>
                        <label>id</label>
                        <item>Optional</item>
                        <label>lang</label>
                        <item>Optional</item>
                        <label>script</label>
                        <item>Optional</item>
                     </list>
                  </p>
               </div>
               <div type="description">
                  <p>Use <gi>seriesstmt</gi> to record and bind together information about the published monographic series of which the encoded finding aid is a part. <gi>seriesstmt</gi> may contain text, formed in
                     paragraphs, or it may include <gi>titleproper</gi> and <gi>num</gi>, which allow for more specific tagging of names or numbers associated with the series.</p>
               </div>
               <div type="availability">
                  <p>Optional, not repeatable </p>
               </div>
               <div type="examples">
                  <egXML xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/Examples" xml:lang="eng" valid="true">
                     <ead:filedesc>
                        <ead:titlestmt>
                           <ead:titleproper>Guide to the Lucretia Mott Papers, 1848-1887 and undated</ead:titleproper>
                           <ead:author>Alice Poffinberger</ead:author>
                        </ead:titlestmt>
                        <ead:publicationstmt>
                           <ead:publisher>David M. Rubenstein Rare Book and Manuscript Library</ead:publisher>
                        </ead:publicationstmt>
                        <ead:seriesstmt>
                           <ead:p>The Lisa Unger Baskin Collection</ead:p>
                        </ead:seriesstmt>
                     </ead:filedesc>
                  </egXML>
               </div>
            </div>